---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { site } from '../config/site';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Chuck Allen"
  description="Privacy policy for chuckallen.dev. How your data is collected, used, and protected."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="prose">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="effective-date"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 8, 2026</p>

        <p>
          Chuck Allen ("I," "me," "my") operates <a href="https://chuckallen.dev">chuckallen.dev</a>.
          This Privacy Policy explains what information is collected when you visit this site, how it's used,
          and what rights you have regarding your data.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Information I Collect</h2>

        <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>When you use the contact form or book a call, you may provide:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Message content</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This information is submitted voluntarily. I only receive what you choose to send.</p>

        <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <p>When you visit this site, certain data is collected automatically through third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time spent, referral source, browser type, device type, screen resolution</li>
          <li><strong>IP address</strong> — collected by Cloudflare (hosting) and Google Analytics</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies and similar technologies</strong> — used by Google Analytics and Cloudflare for site functionality and analytics (see Cookies section below)</li>
        </ul>

        <hr />

        <h2>How Your Information Is Used</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact form submissions</strong> — to respond to your inquiry via email</li>
          <li><strong>Scheduling</strong> — to book and manage consultation calls through Calendly</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — to understand how visitors use the site and improve the experience</li>
          <li><strong>Bot protection</strong> — to prevent spam and abuse through Cloudflare Turnstile</li>
        </ul>
        <p>I do not use your information for marketing, profiling, or targeted advertising. I do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes.</p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>This site uses the following third-party services that may collect data as described in their respective privacy policies:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Analytics 4 (GA4)</strong> — site analytics and usage tracking.
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Tag Manager (GTM)</strong> — manages analytics and tracking tags.
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cloudflare</strong> — site hosting, CDN, DNS, and Turnstile CAPTCHA for bot protection.
            <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Calendly</strong> — consultation scheduling.
            <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Calendly Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Mailgun</strong> — email delivery for contact form submissions.
            <a href="https://www.mailgun.com/legal/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mailgun Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>These services operate under their own privacy policies. I encourage you to review them.</p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>This site uses cookies set by the following services:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_ga_*</code>) — distinguish unique visitors and sessions. Expire after 2 years and 24 hours, respectively.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> (<code>__cf_bm</code>) — bot management. Expires after 30 minutes.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> — session-based challenge data for spam protection.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>No advertising cookies are used on this site. I do not run retargeting, remarketing, or interest-based advertising.</p>

        <h3>Opting Out</h3>
        <p>
          You can disable cookies through your browser settings. You can also opt out of Google Analytics by installing the
          <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-Out Browser Add-On</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site honors <strong>Global Privacy Control (GPC)</strong> signals. If your browser sends a GPC signal,
          analytics tracking will be treated as opted out in accordance with applicable state privacy laws.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact form data</strong> — retained in email as long as needed to respond to and follow up on your inquiry, then deleted.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics data</strong> — retained by Google Analytics per their default retention settings (14 months).</li>
          <li><strong>Calendly data</strong> — retained per Calendly's data retention policies.</li>
        </ul>

        <hr />

        <h2>Your Privacy Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on your state of residence, you may have rights under laws such as the
          <strong>Colorado Privacy Act (CPA)</strong>, the <strong>California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)</strong>,
          or similar state privacy laws. These rights may include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>The right to know what personal data is collected about you</li>
          <li>The right to request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li>The right to correct inaccurate personal data</li>
          <li>The right to opt out of the sale or sharing of personal data</li>
          <li>The right to opt out of targeted advertising and profiling</li>
          <li>The right to non-discrimination for exercising your privacy rights</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <strong>I do not sell your personal information.</strong> I do not share your data for cross-context behavioral advertising.
        </p>
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, contact me at
          <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.
          I will respond within the timeframe required by applicable law.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          This site is not directed at individuals under the age of 13. I do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children. If you believe a child has submitted personal information through this site,
          contact me and I will delete it promptly.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>
          This site is served over HTTPS and hosted on Cloudflare's global network. I take reasonable
          measures to protect submitted information, but no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with
          an updated effective date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or want to exercise your privacy rights, contact me at:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:+1${site.phone}`}>{site.phoneFormatted}</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .effective-date {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* --- Vertical rhythm overrides for legal content --- */

  .legal-page .prose hr {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .legal-page .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .legal-page .prose h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-page .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-page .prose ul,
  .legal-page .prose ol {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .legal-page .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }
</style>
